abstract: Tennessee Titans agree to two-year contract extension with tight end Delanie Walker.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Pro Football; Titans Give Tight End a Contract Extension
headline.main: Titans Give Tight End Delanie Walker Contract Extension

snippet: The Tennessee Titans and the All-Pro tight end Delanie Walker agreed on a two-year contract extension. Terms were not disclosed.
lead_paragraph: The Tennessee Titans and the All-Pro tight end Delanie Walker agreed on a two-year contract extension. Terms were not disclosed.
